  <section>
    <h1>Advisory & Founding Circle</h1>
    <p>The advisory circle provides non-executive, non-commercial guidance, comprising a mix of local and international experts.</p>
    <p>We welcome contributions from Peace Corps alumni, diaspora members, and global professionals with ties to Botswana.</p>
    <p>Advisory roles are distinct from employment, focused on oversight and strategic input.</p>
